Engineering (Michigan, USA): A computer input hardware company founded in 1993, located at 101 Innovation Parkway, Williamston, Michigan, specializes in designing and manufacturing computer input devices, keyboards, and controls, known for products like X-keys, Y-mouse, and RailDriver, registered trademarks include X-keys, Y-mouse, RailDriver, and 'The No Slogan Company'.

Pi Engineering (Calgary, Canada): A pipeline and piping engineering consulting firm founded in 2006, located at 730, 734 7 Avenue SW Calgary, Alberta, specializes in piping stress analysis and finite element analysis, provides engineering services for oil and gas, water, and pulp/paper industries, operates within Canada and globally.
